    "html" :
    
    
    "Cracks in the brake disc friction surfaces are viewed differently to cracks in grey cast-iron brake discs. Cracks in PCCB brake discs do not constitute a wear criterion but exist already in new brake discs because of the way in which they are manufactured."
    
